data.description: Welcome to 5014 Palmer Mill Road! This updated three bedroom, one bathroom home has plenty to offer! Central AC, a large kitchen with quartz countertops and island, stainless steal appliances, and luxury finishes throughout! The first floor features an open floor plan with enough space to relax and entertain. Upstairs you will find three spacious bedrooms and the homes full bathroom. The basement is fully finished and offers plenty of storage space with access to the homes private backyard. Tremendous value and priced to sell! Schedule your showing today while it is still available!
